msgid "Removal Method"
msgstr "Metodo di rimozione"

#: include/global_settings.php:2889
msgid "There are two removal methods.  The first, Standard Deviation, will remove any sample that is X number of standard deviations away from the average of samples."
msgstr ""

#: include/global_settings.php:2893
